  <brief_title>Exploration of the Synovial Fluid Inflammation Mediators Under Diacerhein in Knee Osteoarthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exploratory Study of Some Synovial Fluid Inflammation Mediatorsunder Diacerhein in Knee Osteoarthritis Patients. Phase IV Study.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
