  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Some inflammation mediators, notably IL-1, are implied in the joint degeneration phenomena of
      osteoarthritis. The aim of this study is to confirm in vivo the favourable effect of
      diacerhein on IL-1 and also to appreciate its effect on other synovial inflammation
      mediators.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
